- The following programs are required to be installed:
  - quilt
  - mkimage
- The system expects the following directory structure under the target directory:

  lighttpd-1.4.29/   source:http://download.lighttpd.net/lighttpd/releases-1.4.x/lighttpd-1.4.29.tar.gz
  linux-2.6.29/      source: Provided as course materials

- The toolchain is expected to be located at /opt/arm-2009q1 according to the project specification.
